# Restaurant Reservation 🍽️

A full-stack **MERN application** for managing restaurant reservations.  
Users can book tables online, while admins/staff can manage availability, reservations, and customer details.

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** React.js
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
- **Database:** MongoDB (Mongoose)
- **Authentication:** JWT (JSON Web Tokens)
- **Styling:** TailwindCSS / Bootstrap (if used)

---

## ✨ Features
- 🔑 User authentication (Login / Register)
- 📅 Make, update, and cancel reservations
- 🏨 Admin dashboard to manage tables & reservations
- 🔍 Search reservations by date, time, or customer
- 📱 Responsive design for mobile & desktop

